The purpose of Unit 16 Alky Gas Plant is to process light hydrocarbon feeds from the Crude unit, Offplot storage, or the Reformer for removal of undesired components. This prepares the streams for sale as a finished product or for use as feed streams to the downstream Alkylation and/or Butamer units. This unit consists of the deethanizer, caustic treating shells, depropanizer, butane splitter and LSR splitter.

