The purpose of Unit 12 Sour Water Stripper is to strip hydrogen sulfide and ammonia from sour water. Sour water from the process units is routed to tankage and then fed to the sour water stripper as needed. The H2S and ammonia removed from the stream is routed to the sulfur unit. The unit includes the degassing drum, storage tank and sour water stripper.

